{"tid":1885730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解啲人講極唔撚聽？","createTime":"2020-02-18T13:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T13:19:20.000Z","uid":163235,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf08bdbe27cd91a9794bc228d60f1ee7ee54f4e7","tid":1885730,"uid":163235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:02:17.000Z","msg":"有冇人身邊啲人都係咁7？一邊屌人home office行山、笑人邊爐家族，但自己放工放假睇戲、韓燒、唱K直落！<br />\n<br />\n我屌曬你地老母！講左幾多次，叫你咪撚再去人多地方、盡量減少社交活動。呢啲人又自私又僥倖心態，覺得今次冇事嘅！今日瀨野果幾條友，當日都冇諗過自己肺炎啦我屌！<br />\n<br />\n冇人可以100%sure人地有冇中招，亦唔好覺得自己一定冇！好翻都可以再復發，潛伏期都可以變24日！你憑咩覺得自己今次安全？<br />\n<br />\n知道好多人要翻工或者有自己原因一定要出街。但其他人唔該啦，唱少一次K睇少場洗唔撚洗死！你唔怕死姐，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">但你唔撚好連累屋企人朋友隔離鄰舍，唔撚好增加醫護負擔！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔該生性啲啦！支那狗都識打擊人唔撚好再打牌啊！你唔改變自己啲7習慣，搶幾多個口罩同廁所都冇撚用！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92f5a6ae90d169b16d7e58483e9647093304f8b","tid":1885730,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"結論：樓主無得home office"},{"pid":"1287b492dd53a8f702a920481ab4992bc8480136","tid":1885730,"uid":13936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:04:11.000Z","msg":"結論：樓主無得home office"},{"pid":"5884f1a9763bcc5c0b8ef87b0ed77257c5098409","tid":1885730,"uid":163235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92f5a6ae90d169b16d7e58483e9647093304f8b","tid":1885730,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:03:20.000Z","msg":"結論：樓主無得home office"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"利申：有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd0c77e19be33a72838625340266456955e3ffc3","tid":1885730,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5884f1a9763bcc5c0b8ef87b0ed77257c5098409","tid":1885730,"uid":163235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d92f5a6ae90d169b16d7e58483e964